Class HistoricalStateXto

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.stardust.engine.api.ws.HistoricalStateXto

  • public class HistoricalStateXto
extends Object
    The HistoricalState represents a snapshot of the historic states of an activity instance.
